{
  "title": "Maxema - Icon Pure - Personalized and promotional pens. Promotional writing instruments and custom printed pens.",
  "description": "Icon Pure Minimal lines and balanced forms: Icon Pure is the expression of a design that seeks the purity of simplicity, with no concessions to banality. Icon Pure is basic and elegant, thanks also to the high strength rubber finish that completely covers it, making it aesthetically refined and very pleasing to the touch. For optimal customisation, printing is done before applying the rubber finish, so as to harmonise with the soft touch effect and prolong tightness. If you want to customise the pen when the rubber finish has already been applied, special inks for rubberised surfaces must be used.",
